dialogue.introduction: I'm Inazuma. Pleased to meet you.
dialogue.library_intro: After helping to save the crew of the enemy ship sunk at Surabaya, I fought at Kiska, Solomon, New Guinea and Attu Island one after the other... I did my best...
dialogue.secretary1: Commander, um... you aren't mistaking me for someone else are you?
dialogue.secretary2: I'd prefer not to fight as much as possible.
dialogue.secretaryidle: I really like time of peace like this too, when nothing is happening.
dialogue.secretarymarried: Commander, thanks for the hard work nanodesu. I'll give you a shoulder massage nanodesu.
dialogue.wedding: Commander, you're still here, huh. Eh? You were waiting for me?... Thank you.
dialogue.joining_a_fleet: See how Inazuma is when she's serious!
dialogue.equipment1: It looks like my body has become a bit lighter.
dialogue.supply: It looks like my body has become a bit lighter.
dialogue.docking_minor_damage: I'll go fix myself up a little.
dialogue.return_from_sortie: It looks like the fleet has returned.
dialogue.night_battle: If possible, I'd like to save those sunken enemy ships as well...
dialogue.mvp: I want to win the war, but I also want to save lives... Is that weird?
dialogue.sunk: I wish I'll be reborn... into a more peaceful world.
